rity control over Foodcorp Holdings and Fedfood Omega. As an indivisible part of this transaction, Clidet No.485 will then acquire the remaining minority shares in Foodcorp Holdings and Fedfood Omega, thereby acquiring direct control over the business of F
oodcorp, the wholly owned subsidiary of Foodcorp Holdings. Once these shares have been acquired Foodcorp Holdings and Fedfood will buy-back all their shares held by the Foodcorp Holding Share Trust. Subsequent to this Clidet No.485 will directly hold 49.9%
 of the issued share capital of Foodcorp Holdings and Pamodzi Foods, the wholly owned subsidiary of Clidet No.485, will hold the remaining 50.1%.}
